    "description": "祖国失去尊严，伤害移民——<br>「佣兵烈焰(Mercenaries Blaze)」是以奇幻世界为舞台的<br>战术模拟RPG。<br><br>战斗将在有高低差的俯瞰视角的地图上进行，<br>战斗结果将随敌我朝向为正面、侧面还是背面而变化，<br>根据同伴站位还可得到援助效果，战略性极高。<br>使用战斗中得到的技能点，<br>可习得技能、强化技能和转职，<br>实现高度自由的角色育成。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582510/extras/2e11ce75113d699e85ac4fdd485aa29f.poster.avif?t=1727198405\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582510/extras/2e11ce75113d699e85ac4fdd485aa29f.webm?t=1727198405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582510/extras/2e11ce75113d699e85ac4fdd485aa29f.mp4?t=1727198405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>本作角色由擅于绘制插图和点绘图片的美术师，<br>西村将由老师设计！<br>玩家可欣赏造型美丽的角色们配合喜怒哀乐做出的丰富表情。<br><br>·火热爆发<br>战斗之中，屏幕右上角的槽将逐渐积累，<br>消费积累的能量便可发动「火热爆发」！<br>每个角色的火热爆发效果不同，<br>有的给敌人造成巨大伤害，有的回复全体同伴的无法战斗状态。<br>灵活运用火热爆发便是胜利的诀窍！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582510/extras/2d263a9b7cabd90b9f8d20c86193a043.poster.avif?t=1727198405\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582510/extras/2d263a9b7cabd90b9f8d20c86193a043.webm?t=1727198405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582510/extras/2d263a9b7cabd90b9f8d20c86193a043.mp4?t=1727198405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·3D战斗地图<br>本作为佣兵传说（Mercenaries Saga）系列首次采用3D地图战斗。<br>玩家回合时可随意切换视角，<br>以便更好地观察地图。<br>更换视角还可能发现隐藏道具！？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582510/extras/889ab9252b25aa75fd318865fd3b29e6.poster.avif?t=1727198405\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582510/extras/889ab9252b25aa75fd318865fd3b29e6.webm?t=1727198405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582510/extras/889ab9252b25aa75fd318865fd3b29e6.mp4?t=1727198405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・自由度大幅提升的战斗指令<br>完成攻击/技能/道具等「行动」后，还可以进行「移动」。<br>由此战斗变得更加自由。<br><br>·详细的选项设定<br>选项设定中增加了新的项目。<br>您不仅可以选择3D战斗地图上是否显示网格线，<br>还可使用「技能简易演出」和「移动演出高速化」等<br>让重复游戏变得更舒适。",
